<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I am a level 42 spiritmaster. And i have come acrost a few things that would not only improve the class but the game in general.<BR>#1 Pure casters should have a see inviss buff that can be cast on other players. Why ?<BR>well i think claoking as i like to call stealth, is way too powerfull, I can understand stealth working the way it does now, If the stealther is in a pack of tree's or whatnot, but a valley ? a field ?  this is stealth here, this is blatant cloaking,these arnt hunters, these are predators......<P>#2 i think the ability to give someone else our mana would be interesting.<P>#3 my third issue realy doesnt have anything to do with spiritmasters , so much as it does casters in general on midgaurd. Ever since i saw my first healer i was interested in getting a robe.However on midgaurd we cant were robes,Or even make them/ buy them.My question is tho,why do the Healers and Gothi's in our society have them then ? Is it to tease us ? If your not going to let us were robes, at least remove them from the merchants.... ( and make it a full society thing).<P>#4 the other one that id love to have ( but understand if we dont get) is an aoe nuke, even if it is a spec spell ( aka not as effective) it would still be fun to have one  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>#5 the murk blask spell line... every time we cast it in rvr we are makeing ourselves an easy target.. The waves that emanate from my feet are huge.. Its like im asking to be targeted, it gives me little chance for any kind of solo rvr during the day... <P>#6 please make the pet commands macroable, in other words, the ability to bind my pet commands to macros.<P>#6.5 i need more hot keys too  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"><P>#7 the ability to sumehow pich the race /weapon of my pet. and maybe even gender would be nice. It is however much bigger for the weapon, where as some weapons are better vs some mobs than others are. and recasting a pet till you get the right one eats mana .....<P>#7.5 more pet armor grafics, (aka the diff chain armor grafics for the pets, make it a random thing, the basic chain grafic is old about 3 levels ago ;p)<P>#8 thank you for bothering to read this  <IMG SRC="wink.gif" border="0"><P>Zumgala Tokistada <BR>the self proclaimed Spirit Queen
</FONT>
